verbose_text: To further demonstrate the expression of EMT markers in the cells cultured under normoxic and hypoxic conditions, immunofluorescence staining was performed to evaluate the expression of vimentin, fibronectin, E-cadherin, ZO-1 and HIF-1alpha.
evidence: expression of vimentin, fibronectin, E-cadherin, ZO-1 and HIF-1alpha
